# Steps I used to install Sass

1. Installed Node.js using nvm:
   $ curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
   $ exit
   Reopened terminal
   $ nvm install 20.16
   $ nvm use 20.16

2. Installed Dart Sass via npm:
   $ npm install -g sass

3. Verified installation:
   $ sass --version
   Output: 1.89.1
